{"tid":2414036,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"貝萊德：已開始投資比特幣 | 沈振盈：bitcoin將爆煲 | 歐央行：投資比特幣請做好「血本無歸」的準備","createTime":"2021-02-19T06:22:28.000Z","updateTime":"2021-02-19T15:35:37.000Z","uid":79563,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"f74036034f1a3f70524ccd2df0b546702e835450","tid":2414036,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-19T06:22:28.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://images2.markets.businessinsider.com/5fa5ba9df7d1cb0019e3a548?format=jpeg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimages2.markets.businessinsider.com%2F5fa5ba9df7d1cb0019e3a548%3Fformat%3Djpeg&h=45d2965c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n&lt;匯港通訊&gt; 全球最大資產管理公司貝萊德定息工具投資總監Rick Rieder接受美國媒體CNBC訪問時披露，貝萊德已經開始涉足投資虛擬貨幣比特幣，但強調不會設定投資比特幣的建議比重。<br />\n<br />\n他認為，投資者追捧比特幣，是因為要在超低利率與通脹回升期間，尋找具潛質的投資產品。<br />\n<br />\n貝萊德在1月時披露，旗下兩個基金把比特幣納入可投資對象之一。<br />\n<br />\n根據交易平台Coindesk數據，比特幣突破5.2萬美元，在過去24小時高見52621.84美元，最新報52126.61美元，升5.45%。 (ST)<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=yTk1y1NcyNc\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DyTk1y1NcyNc&d=VW1JDW%2BJF%2FyRlCRofLrhGn9Z9R%2B5WvgLevJIGZbvuGo%3D&h=4d1d6e68\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=yTk1y1NcyNc</a>"},{"pid":"3a0fa8ae5496bc831073d88bcbc5cc1b15b9ecf0","tid":2414036,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-19T06:23:36.000Z","msg":"愛爾蘭央行行長、歐洲央行理事馬赫盧夫(Gabriel Makhlouf)表示，投資者若進場，得為「血本無歸」的後果作準備。另外，歐洲央行行長拉加德(Christine Lagarde)本月曾表示，加密貨幣是「高度投機性資產」。<br />\n<br />\n對於投資比特幣等加密貨幣，馬赫盧夫向外電表示，他個人無法確定為什麼會有人想投資「這類的資產」，但是很明顯地，那些人就是視此東西為「資產」，而央行官員的職責就是「確保民眾得到保護」。他表示，目前比特幣本身還沒有威脅金融穩定的迹象，更該擔心的是民眾是否能作出「正確的選擇」。"},{"pid":"176d6eb1fa0b72a60ced37ad3a72221746c07a86","tid":2414036,"uid":9633,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-19T06:27:54.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"01b86733726ac72f44049c81069a17a6f3a8c3ba","tid":2414036,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-19T15:33:06.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"47d088f3c3af6da76a1c470bd785d1e6d048955e","tid":2414036,"uid":249073,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-19T15:35:37.000Z","msg":"put 125"}]}